<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/9410-ilya"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1512252240i/9410._UY100_CR1,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/9410-ilya">Ilya</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The new Penguin edition is terrific -- it translates the Latin (except the titles of the sources in Burton&apos;s own notes), and the editorial annotations<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The new Penguin edition is terrific -- it translates the Latin (except the titles of the sources in Burton's own notes), and the editorial annotations are great too.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
