        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer107081970" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12569959601177515812">Reality should be snared, at least where it is convenient. Burton demanded browsers and I obliged. I did not read this book sequentially. Nor was any effort made to complete this book cover-to-cover. It was read in a flourish of skips and delights: anti-oedpian piercing and parsing. Gazes, gouges and gatherings, baby. I will return to this for the rest of my life.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


