        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3609259456" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12141230532829227478">Four stars because I found nothing of comfort in the Cures for Love-Melancholy section, but incredible book to latch onto through a seven-month major depressive episode, when it’s read a book or self-destruction, deserving a place on the suicide hotline shelf beside The Book of Job, The Golden Ass, and The Illuminated Blake. I may have been let down, but I’m still here. Thanks Burton! </span>

          </span>
        </div>


